00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:09.360
But do you remember

00:13:09.360 --> 00:13:11.200
what Xu Yang told us before?

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:15.890
He repeatedly emphasized that this hair tie was yellow.

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:17.120
This kid...

00:13:17.280 --> 00:13:19.040
I'm really surprised.

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:21.680
After knowing we suspected hypnosis was involved,

00:13:21.680 --> 00:13:23.200
in such a short time,

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:26.010
he could use a hair tie to plant a suggestion on me.

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:27.520
He's too clever.

00:13:27.520 --> 00:13:28.280
And

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:30.840
even if we investigate him later,

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:33.600
he can claim he was overwhelmed with grief

00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:35.480
or simply misremembered.

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.660
Using that as an explanation.

00:13:39.840 --> 00:13:41.960
A kid who hasn't even finished school

00:13:42.280 --> 00:13:44.480
having such powerful hypnosis skills?

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:46.010
I have good news.

00:13:55.640 --> 00:13:56.770
I checked overnight

00:13:57.480 --> 00:14:00.480
Xu Yang's surveillance records from the past six months.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:02.200
You'll never guess what I found.

00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:03.860
Xu Yang once took Liang Ruqing

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:05.420
to see a psychiatrist.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:21.760
We checked the records in the psychology department's archives.

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:22.960
This patient named Liang Ruqing

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:24.760
did come here for insomnia treatment,

00:14:24.760 --> 00:14:26.090
and visited many times.

00:14:27.200 --> 00:14:28.880
Who was the attending physician?

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:29.680
Hu Li.

00:14:29.960 --> 00:14:33.690
She's the only attending physician in the psychology department.

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:36.330
So there really is someone behind Xu Yang.

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:39.920
Do you have any specific identity information on this person?

00:14:39.920 --> 00:14:42.400
This is an outsourced department that works with the clinic.

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:44.960
The registration information has mysteriously disappeared.

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:46.440
She always wore a mask,

00:14:46.440 --> 00:14:48.360
almost no one has seen her face.

00:14:49.520 --> 00:14:51.640
She hasn't come to work for a long time.

00:14:51.640 --> 00:14:53.760
Planning everything so meticulously,

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:55.560
yet still putting a photo there.

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:57.120
What's that supposed to mean?

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:58.980
Does she think we can't catch her?

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:00.480
Provocation.

00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:04.820
Then let's make her pay for it.

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:10.290
Please take us to the psychology consultation room.

00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:33.960
Captain Luo,

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:35.920
Xu Yang just bought some spirit money

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:36.840
and white flowers.

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:37.640
He went home,

00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:39.100
and now he's out again,

00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:40.720
carrying a container

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:42.260
that looks like an urn.

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:44.120
I understand.

00:15:44.920 --> 00:15:46.720
Today is Liu Yan's death anniversary.

00:15:46.720 --> 00:15:48.320
Where is he taking the ashes?

00:15:49.480 --> 00:15:50.240
Cao Bin,

00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:51.240
stay close to him.

00:15:51.240 --> 00:15:52.560
Report to me at any time.

00:15:52.560 --> 00:15:53.290
Understood.

00:16:14.040 --> 00:16:14.800
Xu Yang.

00:16:15.200 --> 00:16:16.240
Are you crazy?

00:16:16.400 --> 00:16:17.240
Calm down.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:18.240
Let me go.

00:16:19.080 --> 00:16:19.800
Let me go.

00:16:19.800 --> 00:16:20.660
Just calm down.

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:21.640
What are you doing?

00:16:21.640 --> 00:16:22.440
Let him go.

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:23.460
He's awake now.

00:16:30.840 --> 00:16:31.640
Mom.

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:35.120
I've told you everything.

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.850
Why are you still bothering me?

00:16:37.200 --> 00:16:38.320
Every one of you

00:16:38.320 --> 00:16:39.780
is against me, aren't you?

00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:41.000
Xu Yang.

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:42.800
Everything you said,

00:16:42.800 --> 00:16:44.000
we've checked it all.

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:45.360
After all our investigation,

00:16:45.360 --> 00:16:47.120
you're still the prime suspect.

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:47.980
Let me tell you,

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:49.880
you might as well confess now.

00:16:50.120 --> 00:16:52.450
Why would you commit suicide out of guilt?

00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:54.480
Suicide?

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:57.440
What suicide?

00:17:00.280 --> 00:17:01.760
When were you hypnotized?

00:17:06.680 --> 00:17:07.609
A few months ago,

00:17:08.319 --> 00:17:10.319
I met this female doctor named Hu Li.

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:15.420
But she said everything was part of the plan.

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.200
Do you think in my subconscious

00:17:22.200 --> 00:17:23.800
I'm someone who desires to commit crimes?

00:17:23.800 --> 00:17:24.599
What the hell?

